#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "Extending &kate;"
msgstr "Razširjanje &kate;"

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Like any advanced text editor, &kate; offers a variety of ways to extend its "
"functionality. You can <link linkend=\"dev-scripting\">write simple scripts "
"to add functionality with &javascript;</link> or add even more functionality "
"to the editor itself with <link linkend=\"dev-app\">&kate; Application "
"Plugins written in C++</link>. Finally, once you have extended &kate;, you "
"are welcome to <ulink url=\"https://kate-editor.org/join-us/\">join us</"
"ulink> and share your enhancements with the world!"
msgstr ""
"Kot vsak napreden urejevalnik besedila, &kate; ponuja različne načine za "
"razširitev njegove funkcionalnosti. Lahko <link linkend=\"dev-scripting"
"\">napišete preproste skripte za dodajanje funkcionalnosti z &javascript;</"
"link> ali dodate še več funkcionalnosti samemu urejevalniku z <link linkend="
"\"dev-app\">&kate; Vtičniki aplikacij, napisani v C++</link>. Končno, ko "
"razširite &kate;, ste dobrodošli, da se <ulink url=\"https://kate-editor.org/"
"join-us/\">nam pridružite</ulink> in delite svoje izboljšave s svetom!"

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid "Working with Syntax Highlighting"
msgstr "Delo s poudarjanjem sintakse"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For information about adding or modifying syntax highlighting definitions, "
"see the <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/highlight.html\">Working with Syntax "
"Highlighting section of the Development chapter of the &katepart; Handbook</"
"ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Za informacije o dodajanju ali spreminjanju definicij označevanja sintakse "
"glejte razdelek <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/highlight.html\">Delo z "
"označevanjem sintakse v poglavju Razvoj &katepart; Priročnik</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scripting with &javascript;"
msgstr "Skriptiranje z &javascript;"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For information about scripting with &javascript;, see the <ulink url="
"\"help:/katepart/dev-scripting.html\">Scripting with &javascript; section of "
"the Development chapter of the &katepart; Handbook</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Za informacije o skriptiranju z &javascript; si oglejte <ulink url=\"help:/"
"katepart/dev-scripting.html\">Skriptiranje z &javascript; razdelek poglavja "
"Razvoj &katepart; Priročnik</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: development.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kate; (C++) Application Plugins"
msgstr "&kate; (C++) aplikacijski vtičniki"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugins\">&kate; Application Plugins</link> "
"extend the functionality of the &kate; editor itself in any way you can "
"imagine, using the same programming language &kate; is written in, C++."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugins\">&kate; Vtičniki aplikacije</link> "
"razširjajo funkcionalnost aplikacije &kate; sam urejevalnik na kakršen koli "
"način, ki si ga zamislite, z uporabo istega programskega jezika &kate; je "
"napisan v C++."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To get started, see the <ulink url=\"https://kate-editor.org/2004/01/06/"
"writing-a-kate-plugin/\">Writing a &kate; Plugin tutorial on the &kate; "
"website</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Za začetek glejte <ulink url=\"https://kate-editor.org/2004/01/06/writing-a-"
"kate-plugin/\">Pisanje &kate; Vadnica za vtičnik na &kate; spletno mesto</"
"ulink>."

